/* Biography */ new section

Molana Sabir Shah Orakzai is an islamic scholor and motivational Speaker.Molana Sabir Shah Orakzai Haqqani got his earlier education from own village Bagan Kurram agency,after that Molana Sabir Shah Orakzai Haqqani went to Jamia Haqqania Akkora Khattak for higher islamic education.Molana Sabir Shah Orakzai Haqqani belongs to Maktab e ahle sunnat wal jamaat hanfi deobandi.
